oop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-144-\ntools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md:145:**What:** In the evaluation harness (`title-loop.py`), normalize `/` and `:` to a common character before comparing. This accounts for the filesystem character substitution where `:` replaces `/` in filenames.\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-146-\ntools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-147-**Where:** `tools/title-loop/title-loop.py`, `titles_match` function (line 117).\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-148-\ntools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-149-**Current code:**\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-150-```python\ntools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md:151:def titles_match(extracted: str, expected: str) -> bool:\ntools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-152-    if not extracted:\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-153-        return False\ntools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md:154:    extracted_norm = normalize(extracted)\ntools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md:155:    expected_parts = [normalize(p) for p in expected.split(\"+\")]\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-156-    return all(part in extracted_norm for part in expected_parts)\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-157-```\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-158-\ntools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-159-**After:**\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-160-```python\ntools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md:161:def normalize_separators(s: str) -> str:\ntools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-162-    \"\"\"Normalize filesystem-substituted characters (: replaces / in filenames).\"\"\"\ntools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-163-    return s.replace(\":\", \"/\")\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-164-\ntools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md:165:def titles_match(extracted: str, expected: str) -> bool:\ntools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-166-    if not extracted:\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-167-        return False\ntools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md:168:    extracted_norm = normalize_separators(normalize(extracted))\ntools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md:169:    expected_parts = [normalize_separators(normalize(p)) for p in expected.split(\"+\")]\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-170-    return all(part in extracted_norm for part in expected_parts)\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-171-```\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-172-\ntools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md:173:**Why this works:** The expected title `\"saffron wheat buns with quark : cottage cheese (variation d)\"` becomes `\"saffron wheat buns with quark / cottage cheese (variation d)\"` after normalization. The extracted title `\"saffron wheat buns with quark / cottage cheese (variation d)\"` also normalizes to the same. Match succeeds.\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-174-\ntools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-175-**Why safe:** The `:` → `/` normalization only affects comparison, not the algorithm output. No other test cases use `:` in expected titles. The `+` split in `expected.split(\"+\")` happens before separator normalization, so multi-title pages like `FINNISH MILK FLATBREADS + FINNISH POTATO FLATBREADS` are unaffected.\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-176-\n--\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-212-|---|---|---|---|\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-213-| 1. Remove suffix fragments | Failure 1 (Baked Eggs) | Very low — narrow continuation-char guard | `title-extractor.ts` lines 394–406 |\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-214-| 2. Normalize separators in `titles_match` | Failure 2 primary (evaluation mismatch) | None — comparison-only change | `title-loop.py` line 117 |\ntools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md:215:| 3. Hard disqualification for truncated headings | Failure 2 defense-in-depth | Very low — strict cross-match only | `title-extractor.ts` lines 306–308 |\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-216-\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-217-### Expected Accuracy\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/improvement-plan.md-218-\n--\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/9-52aa0c8/feedback.md-38-|---|---|---|\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/9-52aa0c8/feedback.md-39-| `PAPRIKA GYERAN-JJIM` | 1 | All uppercase letters, two words |\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/9-52aa0c8/feedback.md-40-| `NA 3 PAPRYKI` | 5 | All uppercase letters, passes vowel/length checks |\ntools/title-loop/docs/9-52aa0c8/feedback.md:41:| `SKŁADNIKI` | 9 | Polish word, Ł stripped, remaining letters all uppercase |\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/9-52aa0c8/feedback.md-42-| `WARZYWA` | 25 | All uppercase, passes all hard filte