ools/title-loop/docs/16-e59482e/feedback.md-83-- `undefined` (if every remaining candidate in `scoredForThreshold` somehow falls below threshold=0.08 and the fallback returns the highest-scored position-0 candidate, which is the join)\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/16-e59482e/feedback.md-84-- Or `\"Smażona zielona fasolka GREEN BEANS BORKEUM\"` (the contaminated join, when it's the only survivor above threshold)\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/16-e59482e/feedback.md-85-\ntools/title-loop/docs/16-e59482e/feedback.md:86:### 5. `SKLADNIKI` diacritic stripping bypasses section-label filter\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/16-e59482e/feedback.md-87-\ntools/title-loop/docs/16-e59482e/feedback.md-88-A secondary (non-blocking) issue: the OCR text contains `\"SKLADNIKI\"` (without the `ą`). The `SECTION_LABELS` set contains `\"składniki\"` (with `ą`). The `isSectionLabel` normalization does:\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/16-e59482e/feedback.md-89-\n--\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/16-e59482e/feedback.md-103-\ntools/title-loop/docs/16-e59482e/feedback.md-104-2. **Structural bonus misallocation**: When the ALL_CAPS line is a translation rather than the recipe title, `isStructuralHeading` still fires on it, assigning the 0.10 structural bonus to the wrong candidate. The `scored` array (used in the empty-pool fallback) retains this inflated score even after bilingual suppression.\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/16-e59482e/feedback.md-105-\ntools/title-loop/docs/16-e59482e/feedback.md:106:3. **Diacritic-stripped section labels bypass the filter**: OCR regularly drops Polish diacritics. Section labels stored with diacritics (`składniki`, `przygotowanie`) don't match their diacritic-stripped OCR forms (`skladniki`, `przygotowanie` is fine since it has no diacritics, but `składniki` → `skladniki` fails). This allows section headers into the candidate pool.\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/16-e59482e/feedback.md-107-\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/16-e59482e/feedback.md-108----\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/16-e59482e/feedback.md-109-\n--\ntools/title-loop/docs/3-a5a0dca/logs/analyze.log-1867-{\"type\":\"stream_event\",\"event\":{\"type\":\"content_block_delta\",\"index\":0,\"delta\":{\"type\":\"thinking_delta\",\"thinking\":\"off threshold\"}},\"session_id\":\"50e8c58d-ab8d-421b-95b3-3d252643f1a4\",\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"uuid\":\"0ab9323b-63fd-4a51-83ec-3a20bea97f71\"}\ntools/title-loop/docs/3-a5a0dca/logs/analyze.log-1868-{\"type\":\"stream_event\",\"event\":{\"type\":\"content_block_delta\",\"index\":0,\"delta\":{\"type\":\"thinking_delta\",\"thinking\":\".\"}},\"session_id\":\"50e8c58d-ab8d-421b-95b3-3d252643f1a4\",\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"uuid\":\"09f3084b-ac31-4795-94c3-9e87fb79581c\"}\n/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/3-a5a0dca/logs/analyze.log-1869-[Omitted long context line]\ntools/title-loop/docs/3-a5a0dca/logs/analyze.log:1870:[Omitted long matching line]\ntools/title-loop/docs/3-a5a0dca/logs/analyze.log-1871-{\"type\":\"stream_event\",\"event\":{\"type\":\"content_block_stop\",\"index\":0},\"session_id\":\"50e8c58d-ab8d-421b-95b3-3d252643f1a4\",\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"uuid\":\"72e35684-cefc-4cd5-87d4-82e29ccdb0f6\"}\ntools/title-loop/docs/3-a5a0dca/logs/analyze.log-1872-{\"type\":\"stream_event\",\"event\":{\"type\":\"content_block_start\",\"index\":1,\"content_block\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\"}},\"session_id\":\"50e8c58d-ab8d-421b-95b3-3d252643f1a4\",\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"uuid\":\"143d7aea-d13f-48fa-ac17-4d1281cea4ee\"}\ntools/title-loop/docs/3-a5a0dca/logs/analyze.log-1873-{\"type\":\"stream_event\",\"event\":{\"type\":\"content_block_delta\",\"index\":1,\"delta\":{\"type\":\"text_delta\",\"text\":\"Now\"}},\"